{"tid":1453561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"衝出國際！外國文宣網站！","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:00:29.000Z","uid":271864,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aae372e394429e70c29d77ef49bfdd2f463dba5b","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"本人才疏學淺，睇唔過811琴晚發生嘅事，今日倉卒間整咗一個反送中網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://hongkongspeakout.wixsite.com/whatshappeninginhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongspeakout.wixsite.com%2Fwhatshappeninginhk&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=8512c4a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hongkongspeakout.wixsite.com/whatshappeninginhk</a><br />\n（用電腦睇比較好）<br />\n<br />\n但我今日去唔到機場，希望有人可以幫我將佢轉成 QR code 俾遊客scan，打嘅旗號係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">俾遊客用嘅安全地圖，必下載</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">然後將個網站spread出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n同時我屋企硬件太舊，整個咁嘅嘢部電腦已經就快壽終正寢，搞到想整靚少少都唔得，因為部機load唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人可以同我一齊組隊執下/重做反送中外國文宣網站，可以的話加個tg吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"740b05c963d61384b7da81bf8e73f7cb3dcdf63c","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"手機格式傻傻地嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccddda7be3e2e16d551f568adcfda83ebbcf4714","tid":1453561,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1453038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1453038</a><br />\n擺埋上去"},{"pid":"a3d8e1f4700fa3c7c587a7c08fd3ac1976620b67","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"Yuen Long Nightmare嗰度想點彈上彈落"},{"pid":"dc001176cd7507ba58e9cbbdcb55d9096afdee57","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:46:59.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n想組網站小隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240af88ba05ea88f622c99d6ed9365485d1d08cf","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n想組網站小隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1082bd9be66c0370fc213ab9f60e75edf3c2430c","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:16.000Z","msg":"請允許我自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以組隊整文宣網站"},{"pid":"37fcda6131e86f1188d35e1de37eeb9ca202d49c","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9b2c51d70826792c77896f634fbf0968665b47","tid":1453561,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:49:08.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30e711a180